section.para:
Texts can also be represented as sets of word tokens or sets of word types:
&prompt; text_tok_set = Set(*text_tok_list) {'This'@[2w], 'a'@[4w], 'Hello'@[0w], 'world.'@[1w], 'is'@[3w], 'file.'@[6w], 'test'@[5w]}
For example, this representation might be convenient for a search engine which is trying to find all documents containing some keyword. (For more information on why a "*" is used in the call to the Set constructor, see the Set tutorial.)
